    "subHeading": "Step Into the World of Advanced Computing & IT Innovation",
    "description": "The Online Master of Computer Applications (MCA) at Teksversity builds the technical, analytical, and development skills required for modern IT careers. Learners gain hands-on experience in programming, software engineering, cloud computing, cyber security, full-stack development, data analytics, and data science. The curriculum blends academic concepts with practical labs, simulations, and industry projects. Designed for working professionals, the flexible structure helps students upskill while preparing for roles in development, cloud, security, analytics, and advanced software engineering across global tech industries. Not only MCA any course with the best specialisation opens the doors for better opportunities.",
    "keyPoints": [
      "Understand software engineering, coding, and system design",
      "Use tools for development, cloud, analytics, and security",
      "Strengthen logical, analytical, and problem-solving skills",
      "Apply structured and ethical programming practices",
      "Develop leadership for advanced IT and tech roles"
